# SecureBank frontend environment.
#
# The app talks to the backend exclusively through the relative path /api, which is
# proxied to the backend in BOTH dev (vite.config.ts) and prod (nginx.conf). That
# means there is normally NOTHING to configure here — the file exists to document the
# contract and as a place to override the dev proxy target if needed.

# Override where Vite's dev proxy forwards /api (defaults to http://localhost:8080).
# Note: vite.config.ts currently hard-codes the target; wire this in if you need it.
# VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
